                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <p>Columns: 1 ;
                                                  ruled lines: 24;
                                                  written lines: 24; Uniform
                                        layout. Hair side and flesh side of folios
                                        distinguishable. Visible ruling by hard point,
                                        bifolium by bifolium on hair side; ruling by plummet on
                                        other side of hard point.Visible quire by quire
                                        pricking, double for major lines, in outer margins only.
                                        Graphic filler at the end of line. Occasional
                                        infra-linear vocalization. Last written line within
                                        ruling. Initial words, headings and parts of text in
                                        larger square characters. Marginal
                                    notes.</p>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
